{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, by (13), the remaining term corresponds precisely to -L X U.",
    "Equation (19) now follows from ( 14), (15).",
    "□ The twisted harmonic-Einstein equationsAs mentioned before, our original motivation is to produce new examples of invariant expanding Ricci solitons on twisted principal N-bundles, where N is a simply-connected nilpotent Lie group.",
    "In this section we introduce an Ansatz for that purpose, which reduces the soliton equation (1) to the so-called twisted harmonic-Einstein equations (4).",
    "In subsequent subsections we discuss the solutions to (1) in particular cases."
  ]
}